By: Sachal Sarmast
Format: verse
Title: Friend, This Is the Only Way
---
Friend, this is the only way
to learn the secret way：

Ignore the paths of others,
even the saints’ steep trails.

Don’t follow.
Don’t journey at all.

Rip the veil from your face.
